A sample CloudConnector for [ARTIK Cloud](https://www.artik.io/cloud/) to use [philips hue](https://www2.meethue.com) cloud as action target.

You may have to change some configuration parameters for your case.

- This connector(for philips hue) needs no scopes, the permission is configured on the Philips hue page

- This connector doesn't support webhook/notification so far.

- This connector offers you those actions :
    setOn, setOff with parameter lightName
    setOnByID, setOffByID with parameter lightID
    setLevel with parameter lightName
    setLevelByID with parameter lightID
    setColorHS with parameter lightName (color hue and saturation)
    setColorHSByID with parameter lightID (color hue and saturation)
    getState with parameter lightName
    getStateByID with parameter lightID
    getAllStates, no param, get state for all Philips Hue state.

References:

* [nest Developer Documentation](http://www.developers.meethue.com/documentation/)
